Place your ComfyUI workflow .json files in this folder.

When your friends run ComfyUI-Easy-Install-LokeshRV.bat, these workflows
will be automatically installed into:

  ComfyUI/user/default/workflows/Lokesh RV/

How to export a workflow from ComfyUI:
  1. Open ComfyUI in your browser
  2. Load the workflow you want to share
  3. Click the floppy-disk icon (Save) → "Export (API format)" or just "Export"
  4. Save the .json file into this folder

Then share the entire zip (bat + Helper-CEI.zip + this folder) with your friends.
